nodes.text: Lianorm Swamp was a swamp on the planet Naboo close to Lake Paonga. It spread over an area of 85 square kilometers. During the Invasion of Naboo, the Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn and his Padawan Obi-Wan Kenobi encountered the Gungan exile Jar Jar Binks while fleeing from the forces of the Trade Federation.
